title: Trying Everything, Even Lettuce, to Save Florida’s Beloved Manatees - The New York Times
content: Trying Everything, Even Lettuce, to Save Florida’s Beloved Manatees  The New York TimesView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Pollution has killed the sea grass that manatees feed on, and they are starving to death in large numbers. Extraordinary intervention may not be enough to protect them.
